  "name": "RPlog_When_the_Moon_Hits_Your_Eye",
  "title": "A Sith Conspiracy in the Crime Moon",
  "summary": "In the Crime Moon, a brutal hidden bar deep in the levels of Nar Shaddaa, the cybernetically rebuilt Sith Lord Darth Malus meets with the chaotic Lethan Twi'lek criminal Skawn to plot in the wake of the Imperium's arrival to recover the Bantha Tracks. Over an exotic drink, the two discuss how to exploit Malus's recent escape from captivity to throw the Imperium's defenses off balance. Malus proposes two schemes: inserting himself into the unrest on Chandrila to force a public Imperium reaction and sow distrust with the Caspian Union, and exposing Axel Vichten's alleged ongoing piracy to drive a wedge between the Corporate Sector and the Imperium. Skawn weighs in with his knowledge of Caspian politics, Vichten's covered-up crimes, and the CSA's decline, while Malus notes Vichten might yet become a useful asset. They settle on Chandrila as their first target, Malus having already procured a cover ship, and agree to finalize the plan en route into New Republic space.",
